\log\left(\frac{n}{n+1}\right)=-\log\left(1+\frac1n\right)
n+n^2\log\left(\frac{n}{n+1}\right)=n-n^2\log\left(1+\frac1n\right)=n-n^2\left(\frac1n-\frac12\frac1{n^2}+o\left(\frac1{n^2}\right)\right)=\frac12+o(1).
